                  <a class="anchor_link " href="/success-stories/tiger-reserve-india-doubles-its-tigers" ga-on="click" ga-event-category="CTAButton" ga-event-action="click - /success-stories/tiger-reserve-india-doubles-its-tigers" ga-event-label=" Tigers: possibly the world&#039;s most iconic big cat  How we&#039;re helping">How we&#039;re helping</a>
                          <span class="btn share_container" onclick="">
          <a target="_blank" href="https://www.twitter.com/share?url=https://www.wwf.org.uk/learn/wildlife/tigers&text=Tigers: possibly the world&#039;s most iconic big cat"><i class="fa-brands fa-x-twitter"></i></a>
